		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I guess 99% of all games doesn't have batterybackup and doesn't save their highscores. Anyone else but me that's disturbed by this? <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":-)" title="Smile" />
<br />
<br />I was thinking if there's a way of implementing this in a clever way in "our" emulators instead of hacking the game to use battery-RAM?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
