		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Since when is the PowerPak restricted to officially licenced games, let alone games released in the Western areas ?
<br />Does it block TNROM for this reason ?
<br />
<br />Of course not, the PowerPak is a development tool and should support as much configurations as possible. If it doesn't support NROM + Battery backed SRAM then it's definitely a bug.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
